<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Home Page</title>
        <!-- CSS -->
        <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
            integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <!-- JS -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <style>
            /* Aturan Umum */
            body, html {
                font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
                height: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
                color: #ffffff;
                padding-top: 4rem; /* Agar tidak tertutup oleh navbar */
            }

            /* Navbar pendek */
        .navbar {
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(93, 91, 91, 0.8);
            padding: 0.25rem 1rem; /* Mengurangi tinggi padding */
            height: 56px; /* Atur tinggi tetap */
        }

        .navbar-brand img {
            width: 100px; /* Perkecil ukuran logo */
            height: auto;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            color: #ffffff !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 0 0.5rem; /* Kurangi jarak antar link */
            font-size: 0.9rem; /* Ukuran teks lebih kecil */
        }

        .navbar-toggler {
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; /* Perkecil tombol toggle */
        }

        .navbar-toggler-icon {
            width: 20px; /* Perkecil ikon toggle */
            height: 20px;
        }


            /* Section Layout */
            .container {
                height: auto;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                flex-direction: column;
                margin-top: 2rem;
                padding: 2rem 1rem;
            }

            /* Card Style */
            .card {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
                border: none;
                border-radius: 15px;
                backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
                padding: 2rem;
                box-shadow: 0px 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
                text-align: center;
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 800px;
            }
            .card-header {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
                border-bottom: none;
                border-radius: 15px 15px 0 0;
                padding: 1rem;
                color: #ffffff;
            }
            .card-body {
                padding: 2rem;
            }
            .card-body p {
                font-size: 1rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #e0e0e0;
            }
            blockquote {
                font-style: italic;
                margin: 0;
                color: #fff;
            }

            /* Footer (Optional) */
            footer {
                position: fixed;
                bottom: 0;
                width: 100%;
                font-size: 1rem;
                background: #343a40; /* Warna latar belakang */
                color: #ffffff; /* Warna teks */
                padding: 1rem 0; /* Ruang di atas dan bawah teks */
                z-index: 1000; /* Agar berada di atas elemen lain */
                box-shadow: 0px -2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Memberikan efek bayangan */
            }



        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <!-- Logo di kiri -->
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="<%= url %>">
                    <img src="https://logolook.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Loro-Piana-Logo.png" alt="Priboen Logo" style="width: 150px;">
                </a>
        
                <!-- Tombol Toggle untuk tampilan kecil -->
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav"
                    aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
        
                <!-- Navigasi -->
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                    <!-- Navigasi tengah -->
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item active">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="<%= url %>">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="<%= url %>profile">Profile</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="<%= url %>contact">Catalog</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
        
                    <!-- Tombol Logout di kanan -->
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="<%= url %>login/logout"><i class="fa fa-sign-out"></i> Sign Out</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>        
        <section class="mt-4 pb-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <h3>Hi, <b>
                                        <%= userName %>
                                    </b></h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
                                    <p>From the Maisonâ€™s Icons to timeless accoutrements, imbue the festive season 
                                        with a touch of the exceptional and find sophisticated creations to give and keep.</p>
                                </blockquote>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
    </body>
    <footer class="bg-dark text-center text-white py-3 mt-5">
        <p class="mb-0">Tugas PAW Styling Web | Namira Anjani Pramadhani | 20220140081</p>
    </footer>    

</html>